title: Emsisoft Anti-Malware 11.10.0.6563
description:
Emsisoft Anti-Malware V11.10.0.6563


Supported o.s.: Windows 7, 8.1, 10 (32 and 64 Bits)

Emsisoft Anti-Malware is a dual-engine antimalware program. It uses the bitdefender engine together with Emsisoft's own malware engine. it eliminates malware such as virusses, trojans, keyloggers, rootkits, worms, spyware, adware and ransomware.

For 30 days, you will have a fully functional product with realtime protection and surf protection. After this trialperiod you are allowed to use the program as a stand-alone scanner or buy a license to unlock the full version
